                              Class<U> clazz)
        Tries to get the object casted as the target type. If it is generic, the captured types cannot not be validated. Only the base object type is validated.
        Type Parameters:
        U - The type to get the object as.
        Parameters:
        entry - The object to cast.
        clazz - The class of the U.
        Returns:
        The casted object of type U or null if the cast could not be done.

      • getCasted

        public static <U> U getCasted(Map<String,Object> map,
                              String key,
                              Class<U> clazz)
        Tries to get a key from a map as the target type. If it is a generic type, the captured types are not validated. Only the base object type is validated.
        Type Parameters:
        U - The type to get the object as.
        Parameters:
        map - The non-null map that possibly contains the key.
        key - The String key to get the value for from the map.
        clazz - The class of the U.
        Returns:
        The casted object of type U or null if the cast could not be done.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if the map was null.
